like jurisprudence, like philosophy,

00:53:01.920 --> 00:53:04.590
like linguistics and philology,

00:53:04.590 --> 00:53:08.440
even music and literature and art,

00:53:08.440 --> 00:53:09.860
and bringing it together

00:53:09.860 --> 00:53:13.583
with our increasing
